														</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-217ac63 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="217ac63" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<h3>How Menus (and More) Can Optimize Your Food Costs</h3><p>Is your menu properly aligned with existing and emerging consumer dining behaviors and trends that could impact purchase price, frequency, check average, and product preferences? Have you conducted a menu mix, daypart mix, and profit center mix analysis to identify potential opportunities in the last six months? <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/how-to-reduce-restaurant-food-cost">More</a> questions to help optimize costs here.</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0370523 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="0370523" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-image">
													<a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/how-to-reduce-restaurant-food-cost">
							<img width="640" height="211" src="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/how-to-lower-restaurant-food-cost-1024x338.png" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/how-to-lower-restaurant-food-cost-1024x338.png 1024w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/how-to-lower-restaurant-food-cost-350x116.png 350w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/how-to-lower-restaurant-food-cost-300x99.png 300w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/how-to-lower-restaurant-food-cost-768x254.png 768w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/how-to-lower-restaurant-food-cost.png 1314w" sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" />								</a>
														</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3d71a46 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3d71a46" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<h3>20 Most Common Menu Design Mistakes</h3><p>Think of the menu as a piece of real estate and restaurateurs as the landlords. Are all the renters (menu items) paying their fair share? Here are some of the <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-menu-design-mistakes">most common menu design mistakes</a> we see.</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-310592b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="310592b" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-image">
													<a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-menu-design-mistakes">
