														</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-be329d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="be329d7" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<h3>Menu Design to Reinvigorate Your Restaurant</h3><p>Menus are one of the most complex aspects of one of the most complex businesses in the world. Those who’ve made it past a slump have often done so by <a href="https://aaronallen.com/menu-design" target="_blank" rel="noopener">designing a new menu</a> that revisits their brand’s DNA and purpose, in a way that honors the past, but ensures it continues to be relevant today and in the future.</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-73bb3ef elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="73bb3ef" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-image">
													<a href="https://aaronallen.com/menu-design">
							<img width="640" height="577" src="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/design-a-menu.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/design-a-menu.jpg 656w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/design-a-menu-350x315.jpg 350w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/design-a-menu-300x270.jpg 300w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/design-a-menu-500x450.jpg 500w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/design-a-menu-137x124.jpg 137w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/design-a-menu-99x90.jpg 99w" sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" />								</a>
														</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8d2b13d elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="8d2b13d" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<style>/*! elementor - v3.7.3 - 29-08-2022 */
